FBIS3-57820 "drweu002_a_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 AUSTRIA Serb Arrested Trying To Cross Border With Explosives AU0301193294 Vienna ORF Teletext in German 1836 GMT 3 Jan 94 AU0301193294 Vienna ORF Teletext Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Spectacular discovery of explosives at the border checkpoint of Heiligenkreuz between Burgenland and Hungary: It has only now been announced that on 30 December a Serb, carrying detonators and fuses, wanted to enter Austria. The man was arrested. It is still unclear for what purpose the explosives were to have been used. However, it has been confirmed that the explosive cargo is of the same "type" as the explosive found after the double murder of two german border policemen on the "Danube Courier" train.
